(17, 'IDinteractivebuildsmarketingplatformsforalonglistofgreatclientswithcreativeprojectsandcampaigns.OneofthemostfunIbuiltinaquick4weekswas.Thecampaignwasbasedon20millioncodesprintedonOreopackagesthroughoutColombia.Therewere5typesofprizestowininvaryingamountswithatotalof285togive.Noonecodecouldbeconsideredawinnerinadvance,andtheprizesshouldbedistributedevenlythroughoutthe~60daycampaign.Iwrotetheprobabilitytoberelatedtotheaveragenumberofpeopleplayingdailyanddistributedallprizes-bynumberandtype–evenlyuntilthelastday.', 'ugc', 'C:\\DATA\\TaylorMade\\tmt\\application\\views\\projects_table.php', 69, '/eli', 'localhost.taylormadetraffic.com', NULL, 'IDinteractive builds marketing platforms for a long list of great clients with creative projects and campaigns. One of the most fun I built in a quick 4 weeks was . The campaign was based on 20 million codes printed on Oreo packages throughout Colombia. There were 5 types of prizes to win in varying amounts with a total of 285 to give.  No one code could be considered a winner in advance, and the prizes should be distributed evenly throughout the ~60 day campaign. I wrote the probability to be related to the average number of people playing daily and distributed all prizes - by number and type – evenly until the last day.', 'en', 'debug', 1389059452, '2014-01-06 22:50:52'),
(18, 'Asearchagainstthe20millioncodestook.00020seconds,andthesitesupportedbusinessrulessuchasCatpchawhenausersearchedmorethan12timesinaday.IalsoincludedseveralbackendtrackingtoolsandaautomatedQAtestertosimulatevaryingdegreesoftraffic,codesearches,andminimumprobabilities.', 'ugc', 'C:\\DATA\\TaylorMade\\tmt\\application\\views\\projects_table.php', 70, '/eli', 'localhost.taylormadetraffic.com', NULL, 'A search against the 20 million codes took .00020 seconds, and the site supported business rules such as Catpcha when a user searched more than 12 times in a day. I also included several backend tracking tools and a automated QA tester to simulate varying degrees of traffic, code searches, and minimum probabilities.', 'en', 'debug', 1389059452, '2014-01-06 22:50:52'),
