(28, 'AnotherquickcampaignapplicationtogenerateFanPagelikes.TocompeteuserswererequiredtolikeSedal''sFanPage,completeregisration,anduploadvideos,images,oratiponmaintainingtheirhair(ideallyusingSedalproducts;).VotingwasvalidatedbyIP,useragent,andPHPsession,whilevideouploadswerePOSTeddirectlytoapublicYouTubechannelusingtheirPHPSDK.TheprojectextendedID''sforkoftheSlimPHPFramework.Ipersonallyfoundmorehurdlesthanhelpersinthetightlynamespacedcodebaseandodduseofclosuresforrouting/controllers.', 'ugc', 'C:\\DATA\\TaylorMade\\tmt\\application\\views\\projects_table.php', 70, '/eli', 'localhost.taylormadetraffic.com', NULL, 'Another quick campaign application to generate FanPage likes. To compete users were required to like Sedal''s FanPage, complete regisration, and upload videos, images, or a tip on maintaining their hair (ideally using Sedal products;). Voting was validated by IP, user agent, and PHP session, while video uploads were POSTed directly to a public YouTube channel using their PHP SDK. The project extended ID''s fork of the Slim PHP Framework. I personally found more hurdles than helpers in the tightly namespaced codebase and odd use of closures for routing/controllers.', 'en', 'debug', 1389059452, '2014-01-06 22:50:52'),
