(46, '<ul><li>BuildsautomatedreportsonhowpagesarecategorizedbymanydifferentenginesandAPIs,whiletrackingtheweboflinksbetweeneachpage.EverythingisstoredinSQLiteLocalStorageviaLawnchair.Ex.healthline.com/corporate/navigator/stage/crawler.html?domain=sharecareor?domain=healthline(bothtakeawhiletoloadall30Krows)</li><li>Takes.jpgscreenshotsofeverypagecrawled.Itcanalsofirstrenderwatermarksoroutlineallareasofthepagebytargetingcategoriesforeasierreview&amp;debugging.</li></ul>', 'ugc', 'C:\\DATA\\TaylorMade\\tmt\\application\\views\\projects_table.php', 70, '/eli', 'localhost.taylormadetraffic.com', NULL, '<ul>\n                    <li>Builds automated reports on how pages are categorized by many different engines and APIs, while tracking the web of links between each page. Everything is stored in SQLite LocalStorage via Lawnchair. Ex. healthline.com/corporate/navigator/stage/crawler.html?domain=sharecare  or ?domain=healthline (both take a while to load all 30K rows)</li>\n                    <li>Takes .jpg screenshots of every page crawled. It can also first render watermarks or outline all areas of the page by targeting categories for easier review &amp; debugging.</li>\n                </ul>', 'en', 'debug', 1389059452, '2014-01-06 22:50:52'),
