(48, '<ul><li>DashboardaidsinbackenddebuggingoftheHealthlineTaxonomyandsearchdecisions.Italsoprovidesthecrawleradditionalcontrolsforprioritizingareasofthepagetoparse,skip,andflagforchangesorinter-linking.</li><li>ThroughDashboardyoucanrebuildanywebpagewithinaproxyenvironmentonHealthlineserversinordertoinstall,test,anddemonstrateNavigationfunctionalityonanyURL</li></ul>', 'ugc', 'C:\\DATA\\TaylorMade\\tmt\\application\\views\\projects_table.php', 70, '/eli', 'localhost.taylormadetraffic.com', NULL, '<ul>\n                    <li>Dashboard aids in backend debugging of the Healthline Taxonomy and search decisions. It also provides the crawler additional controls for prioritizing areas of the page to parse, skip, and flag for changes or inter-linking .</li>\n                    <li>Through Dashboard you can rebuild any webpage within a proxy environment on Healthline servers in order to install, test, and demonstrate Navigation functionality on any URL</li>\n                </ul>', 'en', 'debug', 1389059452, '2014-01-06 22:50:52'),
