(556, 'AnotherquickcampaignapplicationtogenerateFanPagelikes.TocompeteuserswererequiredtolikeSedal''sFanPage,completeregisration,anduploadvideos,images,oratiponmaintainingtheirhair(ideallyusingSedalproducts;).VotingwasvalidatedbyIP,useragent,andPHPsession,whilevideouploadswerePOSTeddirectlytoapublicYouTubechannelusingtheirPHPSDK.TheprojectextendedID''sforkoftheSlimPHPFramework.Ipersonallyfoundmorehurdlesthanhelpersinthetightlynamespacedcodebaseandodduseofclosuresforrouting/controllers.', 'ugc', 'D:\\DATA\\tmm\\tmtweb\\application\\views\\projects_table.php', 70, '/team?qtfilter=E.A.Taylor', 'localhost.taylormadetraffic.com', NULL, 'Another quick campaign application to generate FanPage likes. To compete users were required to like Sedal''s FanPage, complete regisration, and upload videos, images, or a tip on maintaining their hair (ideally using Sedal products;). Voting was validated by IP, user agent, and PHP session, while video uploads were POSTed directly to a public YouTube channel using their PHP SDK. The project extended ID''s fork of the Slim PHP Framework. I personally found more hurdles than helpers in the tightly namespaced codebase and odd use of closures for routing/controllers.', 'en', 'debug', 1389136657, '2014-01-07 23:17:37'),
(557, 'Atoolforindependentretailerstopublishandtrackpromotions,alongwiththeirreturnedvalueandcost.Forconsumers,LealtadCardprovidesawaytosearchnearbypromotionsandpublishtheirowncontrolledrequestsforgooddeals.', 'ugc', 'D:\\DATA\\tmm\\tmtweb\\application\\views\\projects_table.php', 69, '/team?qtfilter=E.A.Taylor', 'localhost.taylormadetraffic.com', NULL, 'A tool for independent retailers to publish and track promotions, along with their returned value and cost. For consumers, LealtadCard provides a way to search nearby promotions and publish their own controlled requests for good deals.', 'en', 'debug', 1389136657, '2014-01-07 23:17:37'),
