(606, 'Over45GoogleVisualizationGraphscanbecreatedinlessthan10seconds.ByenteringjustafewprojectgoalsintheformofKPIs(KeyPerformanceIndicators),graphsareautomaticallycolorizedintoindicatehowtheyareperforming.Project&accountmanagerscanalsousingasimpleCMSbuiltwithinthereportstocommentonspecificmetrics,addheaders,groupgraphics,changesizesanddrillonthedatathroughAJAXconnectionstoalltheoriginalAPIservices.Thepermissionsmatrixiscontrolledperclient,brand,andprojectwith6levelsofaccess,includingpublishingpublicreportswithencryptedURLs.TheoriginalcodebasewaswritenintheLaravalPHPFrameworkwhichsomewhatresemblesRuby.IhavesincecompletelyreplacedthatcodebasewithCodeIgniter.', 'ugc', 'D:\\DATA\\tmm\\tmtweb\\application\\views\\projects_table.php', 70, '/years?qtfilter=2013', 'localhost.taylormadetraffic.com', NULL, 'Over 45 Google Visualization Graphs can be created in less than 10 seconds. By entering just a few project goals in the form of KPIs (Key Performance Indicators), graphs are automatically colorized in to indicate how they are performing. Project & account managers can also using a simple CMS built within the reports to comment on specific metrics, add headers, group graphics, change sizes and drill on the data through AJAX connections to all the original API services. The permissions matrix is controlled per client, brand, and project with 6 levels of access, including publishing public reports with encrypted URLs. The original codebase was writen in the Laraval PHP Framework which somewhat resembles Ruby. I have since completely replaced that codebase with CodeIgniter.', 'en', 'debug', 1389137941, '2014-01-07 23:39:01'),
