(711, 'Thissystemincluded3levelsofaccesswithtopleveladministratorsbeingabletochangecostvaluesperaccountorproperty,receivenotificationsuponaccountlogins,andschedulingcustomreportstobeemailatanyfrequencyortimespan,toanyone.Thesystemprovidescompletedrillingcapabilitiesonanydatasetforanytimeframe;andpopulatesbothFlexgraphsandDHTMLtablesandchartswithasingleclick.', 'ugc', 'D:\\DATA\\tmm\\tmtweb\\application\\views\\projects_table.php', 89, '/industries?qtfilter=analytics', 'localhost.taylormadetraffic.com', NULL, 'This system included 3 levels of access with top level administrators being able to change cost values per account or property, receive notifications upon account logins, and scheduling custom reports to be email at any frequency or timespan, to anyone. The system provides complete drilling capabilities on any data set for any time frame; and populates both Flex graphs and DHTML tables and charts with a single click.', 'en', 'debug', 1389163378, '2014-01-08 06:42:58'),
(712, 'AGoogleChromeExtensionandbrowser-basedCrawlertoautomateQAofbothsourcecode,flashads,anyJavaScriptinstallation.', 'ugc', 'D:\\DATA\\tmm\\tmtweb\\application\\views\\projects_table.php', 88, '/industries?qtfilter=analytics', 'localhost.taylormadetraffic.com', NULL, 'A Google Chrome Extension and browser-based Crawler to automate QA of both source code, flash ads, any JavaScript installation.', 'en', 'debug', 1389163378, '2014-01-08 06:42:58'),
(713, '<ul><li>BuildsautomatedreportsonhowpagesarecategorizedbymanydifferentenginesandAPIs,whiletrackingtheweboflinksbetweeneachpage.EverythingisstoredinSQLiteLocalStorageviaLawnchair.Ex.healthline.com/corporate/navigator/stage/crawler.html?domain=sharecareor?domain=healthline(bothtakeawhiletoloadall30Krows)</li><li>Takes.jpgscreenshotsofeverypagecrawled.Itcanalsofirstrenderwatermarksoroutlineallareasofthepagebytargetingcategoriesforeasierreview&amp;debugging.</li></ul>', 'ugc', 'D:\\DATA\\tmm\\tmtweb\\application\\views\\projects_table.php', 89, '/industries?qtfilter=analytics', 'localhost.taylormadetraffic.com', NULL, '<ul>\n                    <li>Builds automated reports on how pages are categorized by many different engines and APIs, while tracking the web of links between each page. Everything is stored in SQLite LocalStorage via Lawnchair. Ex. healthline.com/corporate/navigator/stage/crawler.html?domain=sharecare  or ?domain=healthline (both take a while to load all 30K rows)</li>\n                    <li>Takes .jpg screenshots of every page crawled. It can also first render watermarks or outline all areas of the page by targeting categories for easier review &amp; debugging.</li>\n                </ul>', 'en', 'debug', 1389163378, '2014-01-08 06:42:58'),
(714, 'DashboardisaContent-Management-SystemanddebuggingtoolforreviewingNavigator,healthSTAT,andinternalcrawler''sperformanceacrossvariousinstallations.', 'ugc', 'D:\\DATA\\tmm\\tmtweb\\application\\views\\projects_table.php', 88, '/industries?qtfilter=analytics', 'localhost.taylormadetraffic.com', NULL, 'Dashboard is a Content-Management-System and debugging tool for reviewing Navigator, healthSTAT, and internal crawler''s performance across various installations.', 'en', 'debug', 1389163378, '2014-01-08 06:42:58'),
(715, '<ul><li>DashboardaidsinbackenddebuggingoftheHealthlineTaxonomyandsearchdecisions.Italsoprovidesthecrawleradditionalcontrolsforprioritizingareasofthepagetoparse,skip,andflagforchangesorinter-linking.</li><li>ThroughDashboardyoucanrebuildanywebpagewithinaproxyenvironmentonHealthlineserversinordertoinstall,test,anddemonstrateNavigationfunctionalityonanyURL</li></ul>', 'ugc', 'D:\\DATA\\tmm\\tmtweb\\application\\views\\projects_table.php', 89, '/industries?qtfilter=analytics', 'localhost.taylormadetraffic.com', NULL, '<ul>\n                    <li>Dashboard aids in backend debugging of the Healthline Taxonomy and search decisions. It also provides the crawler additional controls for prioritizing areas of the page to parse, skip, and flag for changes or inter-linking .</li>\n                    <li>Through Dashboard you can rebuild any webpage within a proxy environment on Healthline servers in order to install, test, and demonstrate Navigation functionality on any URL</li>\n                </ul>', 'en', 'debug', 1389163378, '2014-01-08 06:42:58');
